    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一群勇敢的冒险者误入一间破旧的密室，四周寂静无声。黑暗中，一个巨大的轮廓若隐若现，被一层陈旧的布料覆盖。好奇之下，他们轻轻掀开布帘，一台满是机关与齿轮的神秘装置映入眼帘。好奇心驱使着他们按下按钮、拨动开关，刹那间，强光吞噬了整个房间。等他们回过神来，发现自己竟然变成了矮胖可爱的弹珠小人！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 《弹珠英雄》！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款创新融合了肉鸽元素的弹珠台战斗游戏。在这里，您将操控您的弹珠英雄，冲撞、斩击敌人机关，穿梭于层层诡秘的地下城，收集强大装备，解锁全新能力。即使战败重来，也无须气馁，凭借坚定的意志、卓越的技巧，以及珍稀的遗物加持，您终将成为真正的冒险传奇！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 撞飞无数敌人与强大魔王，感受复古与奇幻交融的畅快战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/fcea4cf688c98d18088ee159a154814b.poster.avif?t=1770953348\" width=542 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/fcea4cf688c98d18088ee159a154814b.webm?t=1770953348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/fcea4cf688c98d18088ee159a154814b.mp4?t=1770953348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 收集超过100种独特道具，自动触发，助您打造最强弹珠英雄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/00637f983963b5dbfea2aefefee948da.poster.avif?t=1770953348\" width=542 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/00637f983963b5dbfea2aefefee948da.webm?t=1770953348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/00637f983963b5dbfea2aefefee948da.mp4?t=1770953348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与狡猾的地精商人“蛆脚”对决，在五款复古迷你游戏中一较高下，包括弹珠大富翁、老虎机、卡牌对战等，让冒险更添乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/bd7ca67b27bf76aaaa3561c8364e98bb.poster.avif?t=1770953348\" width=542 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/bd7ca67b27bf76aaaa3561c8364e98bb.webm?t=1770953348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/bd7ca67b27bf76aaaa3561c8364e98bb.mp4?t=1770953348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 收集稀有战利品，强化英雄属性，让他们成为真正的战场王者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/a5d4f221c9c468e0d6cf0026ebc2a6e3.poster.avif?t=1770953348\" width=542 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/a5d4f221c9c468e0d6cf0026ebc2a6e3.webm?t=1770953348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/a5d4f221c9c468e0d6cf0026ebc2a6e3.mp4?t=1770953348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由开发团队携手新西兰才华横溢的音乐人Jonny Dyas（乔尼-戴亚斯）精心打造，每一首曲目都让您热血沸腾！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/af198abde212dbcc23caccef07bf0708.poster.avif?t=1770953348\" width=542 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstat